asset.hookText:
New Hampshire for damn sure! The fourth stop on the 0607 North American Peanut Butter and Rail Jam tour struck New Hampshire's Waterville Valley Resort on Saturday, January 13th, 2007. The three rails consisted of a down-flat-down, a 30ft down-rail and two gapped boxes. 

- Music -
Song: "Uh Oh!"
Artist: Riverboat Gamblers
Release: To the Confusion of Our Enemies
iTunes: http://georiot.co/1pSB
